{"tid":2494830,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌細胞與免疫細胞之間的營養爭奪","createTime":"2021-04-18T22:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:15:22.000Z","uid":38861,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb3f10fb7a43d3cfba86af28b50a03b75de2acf","tid":2494830,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:19:51.000Z","msg":"癌細胞所在的環境裡，佈滿各式各樣的細胞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSnvmHQ7UUzbc7EN3xKP8CYR8EtkAxqLQquZENgXLkLTz?filename=4Hwpr2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Hwpr2E.jpg&h=3dbc7641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中有為數不少的是免疫細胞，只可是癌細胞發展出不同的機制躲避免疫細胞的攻勢，因此周遭的免疫細胞並沒能發揮其殺滅不良細胞的功效。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，它們同在一個環境裡，無可避免要面對一個問題，就是如何分配糧食。<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)在癌細胞所在的環境裡，以葡萄糖(Glucose)及麩醯胺酸(Glutamine)為營養界別含量最多的兩大元首。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNzEqLD7CCEGriBtuxTcRtn2q6S3P71n8uYKkc7TqZJWj?filename=FFMMFnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFMMFnG.png&h=1b7d4a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究發現，如果對比單一細胞的營養吸收速度的話，免疫細胞吸取葡萄糖的速度比癌細胞的為快。<br />\n<br />\n反之，癌細胞吸取麩醯胺酸的速度則比免疫細胞的為快。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)重要的是，如果利用藥物阻截兩款細胞吸取麩醯胺酸的話，它們均會啟動機制加快吸收葡萄糖的速度，從而彌補營養所需。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPXUz6aJja8kntDgcPqf1V67Ecj3wxJ4u59TzGaLKSMpT?filename=JfBT4Pp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfBT4Pp.jpg&h=c303e95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n換句話說，它們配備使用及吸收兩種營養的能力，可根據環境供求而隨時變陣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖4)雖然免疫細胞吸取葡萄糖的速度比癌細胞的為快，但如果計算整個環境的吸收總量的話，基於癌細胞數量多於免疫細胞，癌細胞共吸收環境葡萄糖總量達70%有多，而其餘免疫細胞的吸取量則只佔餘下的30%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYsEa5LzaYPdL5wQKReKj6hRyFkauF16QkBdZ6NXsCQLf?filename=NDZndHN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDZndHN.png&h=8a8a3f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦即是說，依靠葡萄糖吸取量來探測癌細胞存在的技術(FDG-PET)，其癌細胞所在的環境至少有30%的訊號是來自免疫細胞，而非癌細胞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=9a8dfd44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=de89bc3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-021-03442-1#MOESM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-021-03442-1%23MOESM3&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=8c0c41a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-021-03442-1#MOESM3</a>"},{"pid":"9588c548983eec300bcf31b81412a0ae2f319723","tid":2494830,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:22:10.000Z","msg":"頂手殘負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7bec32b2e71aa243d7c5c37ac322ba12e2183e","tid":2494830,"uid":38861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9588c548983eec300bcf31b81412a0ae2f319723","tid":2494830,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:22:10.000Z","msg":"頂手殘負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />No problem"},{"pid":"9cc85891fa695547ee9b37a1f6bb20c936b575f0","tid":2494830,"uid":191956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:36:47.000Z","msg":"咁姐係會唔會方法靠平時食嘅野打敗萬惡嘅cancer，例如唔食糖？"},{"pid":"35136e85cec55152b416abb090ce3fab14674320","tid":2494830,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cc85891fa695547ee9b37a1f6bb20c936b575f0","tid":2494830,"uid":191956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:36:47.000Z","msg":"咁姐係會唔會方法靠平時食嘅野打敗萬惡嘅cancer，例如唔食糖？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:12:39.000Z","msg":"三十秒科學&ndash;談生酮飲食作癌症輔助治療的可行性<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2475578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2475578</a>"},{"pid":"21213e4025de5cad27dcac6b96918a0d9e84fe06","tid":2494830,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5deddd6bfee81e4445cddfe7a36ffd849a9aa22","tid":2494830,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T00:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb5f32f046d4bccd28d272d57973cb242dedc47","tid":2494830,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T00:35:16.000Z","msg":"癌細胞真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f05375ca1fdede042142ba76fb071810bd9fa42","tid":2494830,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"即係PET SCAN 會因為咁唔夠準確？"},{"pid":"e05e63f83388e44727906edc7b79a8b94d194259","tid":2494830,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"醯<br />\n連點讀都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473a61704066a35fd2a28a92861db0c3861eb9aa","tid":2494830,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"有冇得整到癌細胞遭病毒/細菌感染"},{"pid":"1678d6a81a9f57b860b3c26653d4a911d7a5fd5c","tid":2494830,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b14073884d738115a7d2bef5786eaddfc7a7d25","tid":2494830,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"工作細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a138ae7e4c4b7fd779e600517e33e3ed0187289","tid":2494830,"uid":27312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdab1ff2d58aa52078572a6243044cb86d67fa5e","tid":2494830,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c44ebd533fedfa06af6bbf5544a6c9d7b2f01c","tid":2494830,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f05375ca1fdede042142ba76fb071810bd9fa42","tid":2494830,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"即係PET SCAN 會因為咁唔夠準確？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:50:33.000Z","msg":"同埋有D類型的癌細胞嗜其他營養而唔嗜糖（例如前列腺癌），而且部分器官本身會吸好多糖（例如腦），依個情況只用PET SCAN嚟量度糖吸取量就唔準。<br />\n<br />\n但PET SCAN可以用來量度其他營養或者癌細胞的標記，可以配合幾種指標量度嚟初步驗證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6eea508a9e00eb97d46036d92b70eb591b34dc","tid":2494830,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"係咪所有癌細胞都可以避開免疫細胞既攻擊？"},{"pid":"173299e71e52ad7a75c1aa5a84c6290002fa33e1","tid":2494830,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}